<plot>An interview with Rick Rescorla, head of security for Morgan Stanley Dean Witter, filmed in his office on the 44th floor of the World Trade Center in 1998. A retired Army colonel and veteran of three wars, Rescorla was killed in the September 11, 2001 attack on the World Trade Center, during which he saved the lives of thousands of WTC employees at the cost of his own life.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?599409</url></doc>
